        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per 10 minutes</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature hits you with an attack.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You're aware of the attack and not @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Off-Guard] against it.</p><hr /><p>You strobe and pulse your brilliant light erratically, throwing off your attacker's aim at the last second with a display worthy of the hottest nightclubs and starriest skies. You become @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Concealed] against the triggering attack.</p>"
